proj3_sec2_summary <- read.csv("../data/proj3_sec2_summary.csv")
library(ggplot2)

2 Submission time summary

submitTime_label <- c("2:37PM", "2:41PM", "3:59PM", "Late submission", "3:37PM",
                      "One day later", "3:06PM", "1:53PM", "3:04PM", "3:28PM",
                      "Late submission")
submitTime <- c(2,2,3,8,3,7,3,1,3,3,9)*60+c(37,41,59,60,37,60,06,53,4,28,60)-(1*60+10)
bar_time <- barplot(submitTime, main="Submission Time: Minutues from 1:10 PM",
        xlab="", ylab="Minutes", ylim=c(min(submitTime), max(submitTime)+20))
text(bar_time, submitTime+12, submitTime_label, cex=0.7)
axis(1, bar_time, labels=as.character(1:11), line=1.3, cex=0.8)
mtext('Team',1,line=3.5)

3 Retrain result summary

3.1 Feature running time

data1 <- matrix(c(proj3_sec2_summary$baseline_feature_time,
                  proj3_sec2_summary$imporve_feature_time),
                nr=2, byrow = TRUE)
bar_time <- barplot(data1, beside=T,
                    col=c("turquoise","turquoise4"),
                    ylab="Time (s)",
                    main="Retrain feature running time")
legend("topleft", c("Baseline feature","Improved feature"), pch=15, 
       col=c("turquoise","turquoise4"), 
       bty="n")
axis(1, bar_time[seq(1,22,2)]+0.5, labels=as.character(1:11), line=0.4, cex=0.8)
mtext('Team',1,line=2.5)

3.2 Model training time

data2 <- matrix(log(c(proj3_sec2_summary$baseline_train_time,
                      proj3_sec2_summary$improve_train_time)),
                nr=2, byrow = TRUE)
bar_time <- barplot(data2, beside=T,
                    col=c("turquoise","turquoise4"),
                    ylab="Time (s)",
                    main="Retrain model running time")
legend(0.5,10.8, c("Baseline model","Improved model"), pch=15, 
       col=c("turquoise","turquoise4"), 
       bty="n")
axis(1, bar_time[seq(1,22,2)]+0.5, labels=as.character(1:11), line=0.4, cex=0.8)
mtext('Team',1,line=2.5)

4 PSNR result summary

4.1 Baseline

err_baseline_claimed <- rep(proj3_sec2_summary$claim_PSNR_baseline, each=20)
err_baseline_retrained <- rep(proj3_sec2_summary$retrain_PSNR_baseline, each=20)
err_baseline_test <- rep(proj3_sec2_summary$test_baseline_psnr, each=20)
type_names <- c("claimed", "retrained", "test")
team_names <- 1:11
err_baseline_all <- data.frame(Team=rep(rep(team_names, each=20), times=3),
                               Type=rep(type_names, each=220),
                               Error= c(err_baseline_claimed, err_baseline_retrained, 
                                        err_baseline_test))
err_baseline_all$Type <- factor(err_baseline_all$Type, levels= type_names)
err_baseline_all$Team <- factor(err_baseline_all$Team, levels= team_names)
(ggplot(err_baseline_all, aes(y = Error, x = Team, fill = Type, colour = Type)) 
+ geom_boxplot(width=0.5,outlier.colour = NULL)
+ ylim(8,30)
+theme(axis.line = element_line(colour = "black"),
      panel.grid.major = element_blank(),
      panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
      panel.border = element_rect(colour = "black", fill=NA),
      axis.text=element_text(size=12),
      axis.title=element_text(size=12),
      legend.text=element_text(size=12),
      legend.title=element_text(size=12, face="bold"),
      legend.position="bottom",
      strip.text.y = element_text(size = 13, face="bold"),
      panel.background = element_blank())
+ labs(title="Baseline Model PSNR", x="Team", y="PSNR")
+ scale_colour_brewer(palette = "Dark2", guide = FALSE)
+ scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Pastel2", labels=type_names, guide = guide_legend(title = "Type"))
+ geom_vline(xintercept = seq(1.5, 13.5, 1), linetype = "longdash", colour="lightgrey"))

4.2 Advanced model

err_improve_claimed <- rep(proj3_sec2_summary$claim_PSNR_improve, each=20)
err_improve_retrained <- rep(proj3_sec2_summary$retrain_PSNR_improve, each=20)
err_improve_test <- rep(proj3_sec2_summary$test_improve_psnr, each=20)
type_names <- c("claimed", "retrained", "test")
team_names <- 1:11
err_improve_all <- data.frame(Team=rep(rep(team_names, each=20), times=3),
                               Type=rep(type_names, each=220),
                               Error= c(err_improve_claimed, err_improve_retrained, 
                                        err_improve_test))
err_improve_all$Type <- factor(err_baseline_all$Type, levels= type_names)
err_improve_all$Team <- factor(err_baseline_all$Team, levels= team_names)
(ggplot(err_improve_all, aes(y = Error, x = Team, fill = Type, colour = Type)) 
+ geom_boxplot(width=0.5,outlier.colour = NULL)
+ ylim(8,31.5)
+theme(axis.line = element_line(colour = "black"),
      panel.grid.major = element_blank(),
      panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
      panel.border = element_rect(colour = "black", fill=NA),
      axis.text=element_text(size=12),
      axis.title=element_text(size=12),
      legend.text=element_text(size=12),
      legend.title=element_text(size=12, face="bold"),
      legend.position="bottom",
      strip.text.y = element_text(size = 13, face="bold"),
      panel.background = element_blank())
+ labs(title="Improved Model PSNR", x="Team", y="PSNR")
+ scale_colour_brewer(palette = "Dark2", guide = FALSE)
+ scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Pastel2", labels=type_names, guide = guide_legend(title = "Type"))
+ geom_vline(xintercept = seq(1.5, 13.5, 1), linetype = "longdash", colour="lightgrey"))
